<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>What is Zero-Knowledge Proof?</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --background-color: #0a0a0a;
            --text-color: #00ff00;
            --primary-color: #ff00ff;
            --secondary-color: #ffff00;
            --border-color: #00ff00;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 700px;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border: 4px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            text-shadow: 4px 4px 0px var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .explain {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin: 30px 0 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--background-color);
            border: 4px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .zkp-animation {
            margin: 30px 0 10px 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        .user, .server {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: #222;
            border: 4px solid var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            position: relative;
        }
        .user:before {
            content: 'User';
            position: absolute;
            top: -28px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .server:before {
            content: 'Server';
            position: absolute;
            top: -28px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .arrow {
            width: 80px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--secondary-color);
            position: relative;
            margin: 0 10px;
            align-self: center;
        }
        .arrow:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            right: -12px;
            top: -6px;
            border-top: 10px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 10px solid transparent;
            border-left: 12px solid var(--secondary-color);
        }
        .bubble {
            background: #222;
            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            margin-top: 10px;
            animation: pop 1s cubic-bezier(.17,.67,.83,.67) 1;
        }
        @keyframes pop {
            0% { transform: scale(0.5); opacity: 0; }
            60% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>What is Zero-Knowledge Proof?</h1>
        <div class="explain">
            <b>Zero-Knowledge Proof (ZKP)</b> lets you prove something is true <span style="color:#ff00ff;">without revealing the actual data</span>.<br><br>
            In this KYC app, you prove you are over 18 <span style="color:#ffff00;">without sharing your birthdate</span>.<br>
            <br>
            <span style="color:#00ff00;">Your privacy is protected!</span>
        </div>
        <div class="zkp-animation">
            <div class="user">
                <span style="font-size:2.2em;">üßë‚Äçüíª</span>
                <div class="bubble">I am over 18!<br><span style="font-size:0.8em;">(But I won't tell you my birthdate)</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow"></div>
            <div class="server">
                <span style="font-size:2.2em;">üñ•Ô∏è</span>
                <div class="bubble">Proof received!<br><span style="font-size:0.8em;">Access granted.</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="explain" style="margin-top:30px;">
            <b>Why is this useful?</b><br>
            - You keep control of your sensitive data.<br>
            - Companies reduce risk and liability.<br>
            - It's the future of privacy and compliance.
        </div>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="button">Back to Dashboard</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
